org.semanticweb.owl.simpleowlapi

Class SimpleOWLReasoner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.owl.simpleowlapi.SimpleOWLReasoner

  • public class SimpleOWLReasoner
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for simpleOWLAPI which provides access to methods for reasoning with OWL ontologies.
    Version:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Kody Moodley, https://sites.google.com/site/kodymoodley/

      • explainUnsatisfiability

        public void explainUnsatisfiability(java.lang.String clsStr)
        prints to console output the explanations (justifications) for the unsatisfiability of a class expression (represented by the given string in Manchester OWL Syntax). Prints 'NOT unsatisfiable' if the class expression is satisfiable.
        Parameters:
        clsStr - a string representation of an OWLClassExpression in Manchester OWL Syntax
